            "heading": "Fielding Percentage Calculator: What It Is and How It Works",
            "content": "The Fielding Percentage Calculator computes a fielder’s defensive efficiency using putouts, assists, and errors. Fielding Percentage (FPCT) measures how often a player successfully handles fielding chances without errors. Formula: Fielding Percentage = (Putouts + Assists) ÷ (Putouts + Assists + Errors)."
